snippet.title: Game Boy Advance - Kidou Gekidan Haro Ichiza - Haro no Puyo Puyo © 2005 Bandai - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Kidou Gekidan Haro Ichiza: Haro no Puyo Puyo is a Puzzle game, developed by Arowana and published by Bandai, which was released in Japan in 2005.
